0:41:57.640,0:42:05.240
Uravuga ngo : "Eh? Nkorera Imana. Ndiyiriza kandi nasenga. Mpora mu rusengero. Ni gute uwo nkuriye,

0:42:05.240,0:42:16.280
uwo nahaye amabwiriza, ashobora kuzamurwa mu ntera akaba umuyobozi wanjye? Oh oya, ni "umuriro"

0:42:16.280,0:42:18.300
Ukirukira ku mupfumu.

