Ukavuga ngo :" Uyu ni uwo nkuriye - yazamuwe mu ntera ni umuyobozi wanjye - Niwe umpa amabwiriza".

0:42:25.780,0:42:28.540
Umupfumu akavuga ngo : "Urashaka ko ngukorera iki?"

0:42:28.540,0:42:31.760
"Mu muriro, mu muriro"

0:42:31.760,0:42:33.660
Bakaguha agafu.

0:42:33.660,0:42:38.720
Kuva yarabaye umuyobozi wawe, ugomba guhanagura ameza ye - ugashyira agafu aho.

0:42:38.720,0:42:43.620
Ubwo ni iherezo.

