Murebe, haracyari kare kuvuga ko uyu mugabo afite umugisha.

0:43:04.760,0:43:09.120
Umutangizi si we nyir'igihembo ariko uwarangije.

0:43:09.120,0:43:15.620
Amateraniro yo ku cyumweru kuri SCOAN

0:43:15.620,0:43:17.480
ayo ni amasomo tugomba kwiga.

0:43:17.480,0:43:28.580
Intwari nyinshi  zirwagwa, abantu bakomeye, abakire....

0:43:28.580,0:43:32.160
Uwatangiye ntabwo ariwe nyir'igihembo ahubwo uwarangije.

0:43:32.160,0:43:43.520
Niba utarangije neza, ibyo watunze bose biragenda hanyuma amateka yawe agasibama.

0:43:43.520,0:43:50.240
Ikibi abantu bakora kirabakurikirana.

0:43:50.240,0:43:58.620
Abenshi muri mwe bateguriwe  abazavuka, nk'intumwa Pawulo -

0:43:58.620,0:44:04.460
bateguriwe abataravuka, igihe bapfuye,

0:44:04.460,0:44:08.680
umurimo wabo uzabereho abantu bataravuka.

0:44:08.680,0:44:12.540
Ibi ni byo tubona ubu.

