Ni gute benshi muri twe; ariko ntwabwo twiteguye kubabara ngo tuzishime ejo hazaza.

0:45:45.940,0:45:55.520
Ibyo munyuramo - kandi mwirukira ku bapfumu - mugerageza gukata urugendo-

