ari ukubategurira ahazaza hanyu.

0:45:58.220,0:45:59.920
Ibyo ni byo navuze.

0:45:59.920,0:46:09.720
Imana ikoresha kenshi ikitu cyose mu kuturinda, kudutegura, gukomeza ubushake  n'ishyaka,

0:46:09.720,0:46:14.460
mu kuduhagarika akanya kugira ngo Itunganye ahazaza hacu.

